<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Batybot - Authorization Complete</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #0f0f23;
            color: #cccccc;
        }
        .container {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #00ff00;
        }
        .success {
            background: #2a4a2a;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #00ff00;
        }
        .token-info {
            background: #2a2a3e;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        code {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-family: monospace;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>âœ… Authorization Successful!</h1>

        <div class="success">
            <h3>Batybot is now authorized and connecting...</h3>
            <p>The bot should now be starting up and connecting to Twitch chat. Check your console for connection status.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="token-info">
            <h3>Token Information (for your records):</h3>
            <p><strong>Expires:</strong> {{.Expires}}</p>
            <p><strong>Scopes:</strong> chat:edit, chat:read, whispers:read, whispers:edit</p>

            <h4>Environment Variables (save these for future runs):</h4>
            <p><code>TWITCH_TOKEN={{.Token}}</code></p>
            <p><code>TWITCH_REFRESH={{.Refresh}}</code></p>
            <p><code>TWITCH_EXPIRES={{.ExpiresRaw}}</code></p>
        </div>

        <p><em>You can safely close this tab now. The bot will continue running in the background.</em></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
